re available in our <italic toggle="yes">H. salinarum</italic> NRC-1 multi-omics atlas portal (<ext-link xlink:href="https://halodata.systemsbiology.net" ext-link-type="uri">https://halodata.systemsbiology.net</ext-link>).</p>
